ymmetrically poor reward-to-risk. Wait for either: (a) a short-covering bounce to $3,300-$3,500 range to re-enter short with better entry and reduced crowding, or (b) a confirmed break below $3,000 with a short-squeeze exhaustion signal before adding exposure. Current entry is high-risk, low-reward, consensus, and poorly timed.
